OL,3,CInflation rises to 2.2% in first
OL,4,Cincrease this year
OL,6,FCPI rose by 2.2% in the 12 months to
OL,7,FJuly 2024, up from 2% in June 2024,
OL,8,Fmainly driven by prices of gas and
OL,9,Felectricity falling by less than a
OL,10,Fyear ago, the Office for National
OL,11,FStatistics (ONS) said.
OL,13,FThis is the first increase in
OL,14,Finflation since last December when
OL,15,Finflation was 4%.
