OL,6,FResponding to the figures, chief
OL,7,Fsecretary to the Treasury Darren
OL,8,FJones, said: "The new government is
OL,9,Funder no illusion as to the scale of
OL,10,Fthe challenge we have inherited, with
OL,11,Fmany families still struggling with
OL,12,Fthe cost of living.
OL,14,F"That is why we are taking the tough
OL,15,Fdecisions now to fix the foundations
OL,16,Fof our economy so we can rebuild
OL,17,FBritain and make every part of the
OL,18,Fcountry better off."
