OL,6,FShe said: "The government needs to
OL,7,Ftackle the cost-of-living crisis head-
OL,8,Fon, starting by investing in our
OL,9,Ffarmers to bring down food prices,
OL,10,Fsaving families money by expanding
OL,11,Ffree school meals to all children in
OL,12,Fpoverty and implementing a one-year
OL,13,Ffreeze to rail fares."
OL,15,FNew researched has showed that the
OL,16,Fcost of the cheapest groceries jumped
OL,17,Fmore sharply than more premium brands,
OL,18,Fadding to the pressure poorer
OL,19,Fhouseholds face.
