OL,6,FThat prompted the Bank to raise
OL,7,Finterest rates to a 16-year high of
OL,8,F5.25% last year, which it only cut for
OL,9,Fthe first time since then this month,
OL,10,Fin a quarter-point drop to 5%.
OL,12,FThe Bank of England said on August 1
OL,13,Fthat the fall-away of energy bills in
OL,14,Fthe wider inflation figures would show
OL,15,F"more clearly the prevailing
OL,16,Fpersistence of domestic inflationary
OL,17,Fpressures".
OL,19,FThe latest rise will likely affect the
OL,20,FBank of England's decision on whether
OL,21,Fto cut interest further.
