OL,3,CInflation rises to 2.2% in first
OL,4,Cincrease this year
OL,6,FOfficials expect inflation will
OL,7,Fcontinue to nudge up for the rest of
OL,8,F2024 before falling gradually again.
OL,10,FThe closely-watched annual rate of CPI
OL,11,Fservices price inflation fell to 5.2%
OL,12,Fin July, down from 5.7% in June, its
OL,13,Flowest rate since June 2022.
OL,15,FExperts have warned that persistently
OL,16,Fhigh services price inflation could
OL,17,Frisk pushing the overall inflation
OL,18,Fdata up further, but the drop could
OL,19,Fprovide some encouragement to
OL,20,Fpolicymakers.
